  <rte>
    <name>Lonscale Fell and Latrigg from Underscar Lane</name>
    <desc>Many fells are ignored because there are higher and seemingly grander fells close by. This Lake District walk combines one of these, Lonscale Fell, with a very popular lower fell, namely Latrigg.</desc>
	<author>Copyright Walking Britain</author>
	<url>www.walkingbritain.co.uk/walk-1244-description</url>
